"you can add a menu entry for the program <application>gnucash</application> "
"(see <ulink type=\"help\" url=\"ghelp:user-guide#menu-editor\">the menu "
"editor manual</ulink> for help on how to add menu entries)."
msgstr ""
"Você pode abrir o <application>GnuCash</application>, executando o comando "
"<application>gnucash</application> (veja <ulink type=\"help\" "
